FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780038278
OL,3,CLeukaemia survivor urges more stem
OL,4,Ccell donors to sign up
OL,6,FMore than a decade later, Anie is now
OL,7,Fsharing her story to encourage more
OL,8,Fpeople from South Asian and Black
OL,9,Fcommunities to join the UK stem cell
OL,10,Fdonor register.
OL,12,FAfter weeks of feeling unwell, Anie's
OL,13,Ffather insisted she get a blood test.
OL,14,FThat same night, doctors arrived at
OL,15,Fher family home in the early hours of
OL,16,Fthe morning.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780038278
OL,3,CLeukaemia survivor urges more stem
OL,4,Ccell donors to sign up
OL,6,F"Actually, that night, at three
OL,7,Fo'clock in the morning, we had a
OL,8,Fdoctor show up to the house with
OL,9,Fflashing lights and saying that I need
OL,10,Fto go to hospital now because it is a
OL,11,Flife or death situation," she said.
OL,13,FDoctors soon confirmed she had
OL,14,Fleukaemia.
OL,16,F"My dad was stood on my left shoulder
OL,17,Fand my mum was stood in the corner and
OL,18,Fhe was trembling and the doctors told
OL,19,Fme that I had leukaemia and the first
OL,20,Fthing I remember saying was, 'Am I
OL,21,Fgoing to die?'"
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@YO]xD@AOU}D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780038278
OL,3,CLeukaemia survivor urges more stem
OL,4,Ccell donors to sign up
OL,6,FOver the next two years, Anie
OL,7,Funderwent chemotherapy, antibody
OL,8,Ftherapy and repeated hospital
OL,9,Ftreatment. At one point, she dropped
OL,10,Fto just five stone.
OL,12,FEventually, doctors told her a stem
OL,13,Fcell transplant was her best chance of
OL,14,Fsurvival.
OL,16,FBut finding a donor match proved
OL,17,Fdifficult.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780038278
OL,3,CLeukaemia survivor urges more stem
OL,4,Ccell donors to sign up
OL,6,F"One of my friends in the bay next to
OL,7,Fme - she was a white girl - and she
OL,8,Fwas told she would need a stem cell
OL,9,Ftransplant and the next day the
OL,10,Fdoctors came to her and said that she
OL,11,Fhad four 10 out of 10 matches on the
OL,12,Fregister," Anie said.
OL,14,F"She could basically pick and choose
OL,15,Fand she was going to survive. But I
OL,16,Flooked at the calendar and I was
OL,17,Fwaiting for over eight months and
OL,18,Fthere was not one match that was over
OL,19,Fsix out of ten for me."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@JO]vD@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780038278
OL,3,CLeukaemia survivor urges more stem
OL,4,Ccell donors to sign up
OL,6,FPatients are more likely to find a
OL,7,Fstem cell match from somebody with a
OL,8,Fsimilar ethnic background, but people
OL,9,Ffrom South Asian and Black communities
OL,10,Fremain underrepresented on donor
OL,11,Fregisters across the UK.
OL,13,FAfter months of waiting, Anie finally
OL,14,Freceived a stem cell transplant. It
OL,15,Fwas successful.
OL,17,FCharities say many people are still
OL,18,Funaware of how straightforward stem
OL,19,Fcell donation can be.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780038278
OL,3,CLeukaemia survivor urges more stem
OL,4,Ccell donors to sign up
OL,6,FMost donations are carried out through
OL,7,Fa process similar to giving blood,
OL,8,Fwhile joining the register usually
OL,9,Fonly requires a simple cheek swab.
OL,11,FSome charities, including Anthony
OL,12,FNolan, focus on younger donors aged
OL,13,Fbetween 16 and 30 because younger stem
OL,14,Fcells are linked to better transplant
OL,15,Foutcomes. Meanwhile, DKMS accepts
OL,16,Fdonors up to the age of 55.
OL,18,FZaffer Khan, CEO of One Voice Charity
OL,19,Fin Blackburn, said more awareness is
OL,20,Furgently needed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780038278
OL,3,CLeukaemia survivor urges more stem
OL,4,Ccell donors to sign up
OL,6,F"A match in the indigenous community
OL,7,Fcan be fairly straightforward. But in
OL,8,Fsome of our communities it can be
OL,9,Fthree or four times as unlikely to
OL,10,Ffind a match," he said.
OL,12,F"I think those statistics show that we
OL,13,Fhave got a lot more to do."
OL,15,FThe charity works with communities
OL,16,Facross Blackburn to encourage more
OL,17,Fpeople from diverse backgrounds to
OL,18,Fsign up.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@NO]tD@AOUuD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780038278
OL,3,CLeukaemia survivor urges more stem
OL,4,Ccell donors to sign up
OL,6,FNazia Khan, health manager at One
OL,7,FVoice Blackburn, said many fears
OL,8,Faround donation come from
OL,9,Fmisinformation.
OL,11,F"They just take the blood out of your
OL,12,Fbody, put it into a machine, filter
OL,13,Fyour stem cells and they actually put
OL,14,Fthat blood back into your body so you
OL,15,Faren't losing anything," she said.
OL,17,F"No anaesthetics, no staying overnight
OL,18,Fat hospital, so I think that really
OL,19,Freassures them as well."
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@XO]yD@AOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780038278
OL,3,CLeukaemia survivor urges more stem
OL,4,Ccell donors to sign up
OL,6,FFor Anie, increasing the number of
OL,7,Fpeople on the stem cell register could
OL,8,Fmean more families getting the outcome
OL,9,Fhers did.
OL,11,F"It's just so important to sign up,"
OL,12,Fshe said.
OL,14,F"I'm able to show you loads of friends
OL,15,Fwho I'm here with today who have made
OL,16,Fit because of the stem cell register,
OL,17,Fbut the flip side of that is that I've
OL,18,Fgot loads of friends who aren't here
OL,19,Ftoday because they didn't get those
OL,20,Fmatches.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@dO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
