FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780038278
OL,3,CLeukaemia survivor urges more stem
OL,4,Ccell donors to sign up
OL,6,F"That's why it's so important. We need
OL,7,Fmore people to sign up so people can
OL,8,Fmake it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@IO]
